|8 |    │   └─TABLE FULL SCAN |u    |3       |3           |
|9 |    └─SUBPLAN SCAN        |VIEW1|4       |4           |
|10|      └─HASH GROUP BY     |     |4       |4           |
|11|        └─TABLE FULL SCAN |o    |4       |3           |
===========================================================
